{"tid":1584582,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"前曼聯金童安達臣退役","createTime":"2019-09-21T07:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T00:02:36.000Z","uid":153600,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"b8802686a9d386566ed7cd9e5c6a6cd3f460937b","tid":1584582,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:57:16.000Z","msg":"Former Golden Boy and Man Utd midfielder Anderson retires at 31<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe Brazilian never reached the heights of his early promise and hangs up his boots after a spell in Turkey<br />\n<br />\nTurkish club&nbsp;Adana Demirspor have revealed that former&nbsp;Manchester United&nbsp;midfielder Anderson has retired from playing football.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nThe Brazilian moved to&nbsp;Turkey&nbsp;in 2018 but&nbsp;has&nbsp;apparently decided against playing on this season at the age of just 31.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nAccording to&nbsp;Adana Demirspor's chairman Murat Sancak, Anderson will remain with the club in an off-field&nbsp;position and has taken a significant pay cut in the process. (<a href=\"http://goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoal.com&d=ekRw3fL0jih6ME0SbOEd7258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=683fa7c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"1a0d47c7e88926213efad92ac7aed5bde404478a","tid":1584582,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:58:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"a6cce736937fdc569ce0438b0d89745efa333d20","tid":1584582,"uid":6577,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:58:44.000Z","msg":"Wfc"},{"pid":"ee28843c66e0ab71943b7ec78fda614077f6a594","tid":1584582,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":